eu.kartoffelquadrat.xoxinternals.service

Class XoxClaimFieldAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tpiggo.xoxinternals.service.XoxClaimFieldAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Action

    public class XoxClaimFieldAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Action
    Represents the only kind of blackboard action required in Xox. The Claim-Field action encodes a position, specified through x and y coordinates and a player who claims the field. The origin is top-left, index counting starts at 0.
    Author:
    Maximilian Schiedermeier
